  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardCategoriesAdapter
    This adapter class populates cards related to categories in the Featured Categories section of the Home page.
    CardCategoriesAdapter.CardViewHolder
    Holder class to contain all the views required during populating content into it.
    CardViewAdapter
    An Adapter class, which populates cards related to apps in various activities like HomeActivity, AppsActivity etc.
    CardViewAdapter.CardViewHolder
    Holder class to contain all the views required during populating content into it.
    CategoriesAdapter
    This adapter class populates cards related to categories in the Categories Activity.
    CategoriesAdapter.CategoriesViewHolder
    Holder class to contain all the views required during populating content into it.
    FullScreenImageAdapter
    An adapter class which populates a full screen image for the screenshots to be viewed better.
    MyAppsViewAdapter
    This adapter class populates cards related to apps in the My-Apps section of the Home Page.
    MyAppsViewAdapter.MyAppsViewHolder
    Holder class to contain all the views required during populating content into it.
    SearchListAdapter
    An adapter class for the search list suggestions.
    ViewPagerAdapter
    This is an adapter class which populates the fragments(Store and My-Apps) in the Home Page.
